  • Field Details

    • POST_FROM_COLLECTION

      public static final String POST_FROM_COLLECTION
      Set this parameter to true in a resource controller method where the HTTP POST method is used to create a new resource. The sample usage in a resource controller method is as below:
      Map<String, Object> otherParams = new HashMap<String, Object>(); otherParams.put(ViewParams.POST_FROM_COLLECTION, true); return getRenderedObject(repositoryName, newFolderLink, true, uriInfo, otherParams);
